text: On 26 June 2022, at least 21 people died during a celebration at the Enyobeni Tavern, a nightclub in East London, Eastern Cape, South Africa. Four more people were injured. No causes of death have been found. ==References== Category:2022 disasters in Africa Category:2020s in South Africa Category:Disasters in buildings and structures Category:Eastern Cape Category:June 2022 events
title: Enyobeni Tavern disaster
